Italy Recalls Its Ambassador to Iran, Foreign Minister Giulio Terzi Says

-- B y   L o r e n z o   T o t a r o
-- 
2011-12-01T15:35:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-01/italy-recalls-its-ambassador-to-iran-foreign-minister-giulio-terzi-says.html
Italy has recalled its ambassador to
 Iran , Foreign Minister Giulio Terzi said.  He made the announcement in Brussels today after a meeting
of European Union foreign ministers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
